        "title": "Add compact mode for QA profile evidence",
        "body": "## Summary\n- add taxonomy profile `evidenceMode: full | compact`, set `smoke-ci` to compact, and emit top-level `isCompact` in `qa-evidence.json`\n- thread compact/full mode through profile dispatch, suite evidence writers, unified test-file partitions, and scorecard attachment so `--evidence-mode full` preserves execution metadata for compact profiles\n- add `qa run --evidence-mode <full|compact>` for profile runs and keep `--exclude-test-execution-evidence` as a hidden compact alias\n- update QA docs so operators can distinguish full evidence entries from intentionally compact profile artifacts\n\n## Verification\n- `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs extensions/qa-lab/src/cli.test.ts extensions/qa-lab/src/cli.runtime.test.ts extensions/qa-lab/src/evidence-summary.test.ts extensions/qa-lab/src/suite-launch.runtime.test.ts extensions/qa-lab/src/live-transports/whatsapp/cli.runtime.test.ts`\n- `pnpm tsgo:prod`\n- `pnpm tsgo:test:extensions`\n- `pnpm lint:extensions`\n- `pnpm docs:list`\n- `pnpm docs:check-mdx`\n- `pnpm format:docs:check`\n- `git diff --check`\n- `pnpm exec oxfmt --check extensions/qa-lab/src/cli.runtime.test.ts extensions/qa-lab/src/cli.runtime.ts extensions/qa-lab/src/cli.test.ts extensions/qa-lab/src/cli.ts extensions/qa-lab/src/evidence-summary.test.ts extensions/qa-lab/src/evidence-summary.ts extensions/qa-lab/src/live-transports/whatsapp/cli.runtime.test.ts extensions/qa-lab/src/scorecard-evidence.ts extensions/qa-lab/src/scorecard-taxonomy.ts extensions/qa-lab/src/suite-launch.runtime.test.ts extensions/qa-lab/src/suite-launch.runtime.ts extensions/qa-lab/src/suite.ts extensions/qa-lab/src/test-file-scenario-runner.ts`\n- `.agents/skills/autoreview/scripts/autoreview --mode local`\n",
